hould de-</div><div class="t ma50 x45 h4 ya38 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mand a plain &apos;Thus saith the Lord&apos; in its </div><div class="t m5c3 x45 h4 y9e1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">support.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m12f0 xb2 h30 y1473 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Great Controversy, </div><div class="t m18c3 x195 h4 y1473 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">page </div><div class="t m99d x45 h4 y5e1 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">595. </div><div class="t me4 x21 h27 y69f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">10. </div><div class="t maa3 x9 h27 y69f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Even if a false prophet should </div><div class="t m1bf x45 h27 yd8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perform a miracle, upon what basis </div><div class="t m351 x45 h27 ydea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">may his authority be denied? Deut. </div><div class="t m802 x45 h27 y5eb ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13:1-4. </div><div class="t me4 x21 h27 y5d2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">11. </div><div class="t mae0 x9 h27 y5d2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In view of the activities of coun-</div><div class="t m1142 x20 h27 y1f8 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terfeit christs, how may Christians rec-</div><div class="t m43d x20 h27 y1bc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ognize the coming of the true Son of </div><div class="t m2f8 x20 h27 y38b ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God? Matt. 24:24-27; 25:31. Compare </div><div class="t m322 x20 h27 y4cc ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1 Thess. 4:16, 17; Rev. 1:7. </div><div class="t m235 xbc h4 y49a ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NoTE.—&quot;Satan is not permitted to coun-</div><div class="t mb6f x58 h4 y606 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terfeit the manner of Christ&apos;s advent. . . . </div><div class="t mdd9 x20 h4 y2c2 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This coming, there is no possibility of coun-</div><div class="t m5a1 x20 h4 y48e ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terfeiting. It will be universally known—</div><div class="t me29 x20 h4 ya59 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">witnessed by the whole world.&quot;—The </div><div class="t m190c x1a3 h30 y80c ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0"